  "reference_map_note": "babok_source_refs are drawn directly from IIBA's official ECBA Reference Map. babok_ref uses the BABOK Guide's own chapter.task numbering (e.g. BABOK task '3.1 Plan Business Analysis Approach'), which is a DIFFERENT numbering system from this file's activity_statement id (e.g. ECBA '9.4'). The two numbering systems coincidentally overlap in places (both start counting near '3.1') but are otherwise unrelated -- do not assume any pattern between an activity_statement id and a babok_ref.",
